icc_presiding_officer.body:
A new POSH complaint ({{complaintNumber}}) has been submitted and assigned to the ICC.

Category: {{category}}
Severity: {{severity}}
Criminal Threshold: {{criminalThreshold}}

Please acknowledge within {{deadlineDays}} days. Failure to acknowledge will trigger automatic escalation.

View details in the Rakshak ICC Dashboard.

escalation_contacts_level_1.body:
This is an automated escalation from the Rakshak workplace safety system.

POSH complaint {{complaintNumber}} was submitted on {{submittedDate}} but the Internal Complaints Committee failed to acknowledge it within the required {{deadlineDays}}-day window.

Per Section 4 of the POSH Act, 2013, the Audit Committee is requested to intervene and ensure the complaint is addressed.

Complaint Summary:
- Category: {{category}}
- Severity: {{severity}}
- Days since submission: {{daysSinceSubmission}}

escalation_contacts_level_2.body:
This is a final automated escalation from the Rakshak workplace safety system.

POSH complaint {{complaintNumber}} has not been addressed by either the Internal Complaints Committee or the Audit Committee.

Timeline:
- Submitted: {{submittedDate}}
- ICC deadline missed: {{deadlineDate}}
- Escalated to Audit Committee: {{auditEscalationDate}}
- Audit Committee failed to act

Per Section 6 of the POSH Act, 2013, the District Officer is requested to constitute a Local Complaints Committee or take appropriate action.

icc_presiding_officer.body:
URGENT: Only {{daysRemaining}} days remain to complete the inquiry for complaint {{complaintNumber}}.

Deadline: {{inquiryDeadlineDate}}

Failure to complete within the statutory 90-day window will be logged and may trigger escalation.

Complaint {{complaintNumber}} has been flagged as potentially crossing from workplace harassment (POSH Act) into criminal conduct under the Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita, 2023.

Applicable BNS Sections: {{bnsSections}}

Per Section 19(d) of the POSH Act, the employer is obligated to assist the complainant in filing a police complaint if requested. Please review and take appropriate action.
